The paper deals with image understanding using neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (cs.CL) for generating and answering questions. The use of recurrent neural networks (RNN) and convolutional neural networks (CNN) also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the evaluation of the proposed method involves subjective human judgments, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR).
